&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/akihi878/akihi878.github.io&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
